sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Premium User
    participant FE as React<br/>CustomVisualizationPage
    participant API as DRF<br/>AlertAnalyticsView
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Configure chart (select metric, dimensions, chart type)
    FE->>API: GET /api/analytics/?metric=protocol&dimension=time&chart=line&range=30d
    API->>DB: Alert.objects.filter(timestamp__gte=start)
    API->>DB: .values("protocol", "timestamp__date").annotate(Count)
    DB-->>API: Time-series aggregation
    API-->>FE: 200 OK {labels, datasets: [{label: "TCP", data: [...]}, ...]}
    FE->>FE: Render Recharts Line/Bar/Pie chart
    FE-->>U: Display custom time-series visualization
